Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.70,0:00:09.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,The countless flowers,\Nenveloped in light...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.75,0:00:20.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,...gaze at tomorrow\Nwith unwavering eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.34,0:00:39.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,Everyone wishes for me to be pure...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.35,0:00:46.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,...but what can I bring\Nwith me to the frayed skies?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.81,0:00:53.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,What I've made my own\Nby breaking off flowers in bloom...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.90,0:00:59.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,All such sinful things...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.50,0:01:06.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why did I stop making\Npromises with the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.98,0:01:14.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because even if I try\Nto run far from all the pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.28,0:01:20.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,...a cold wind rustles\Nmy hair... Don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.99,0:01:28.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Where can I ever find the answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.66,0:02:09.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril, more... More powerful, Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.10,0:02:16.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril, don't look! You can't\Nkill them if you see their eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.49,0:02:20.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.38,0:02:40.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,Amuria!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.90,0:02:47.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Amuria!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.41,0:03:15.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wounds and Pain
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.09,0:03:25.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, Alty. Chase those birds. Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.78,0:03:28.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're on duty right now, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.60,0:03:32.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,So what? We won't\Nrun into the enemy here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.28,0:03:35.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,You'll just miss out\Nif you're so wound up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.85,0:03:38.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess you're\Nright about that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.95,0:03:46.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,They've been flying by us awhile.\NI wonder where they're headed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.10,0:03:50.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,They can't fly forever. They'll rest\Ntheir wings when they're tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.27,0:03:53.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,They've got to eat\Nwhen they get hungry, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.47,0:04:00.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,What are they doing? We're on duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.05,0:04:12.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Things seem pretty\Nmellow these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.62,0:04:14.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.00,0:04:18.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,We finally returned to duty too.\NWe seem to have lost our edge.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.30,0:04:21.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,And Aer never\Nvolunteers to fly anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.90,0:04:26.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Para-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.03,0:04:30.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,How's Sibylla Aurea\Ndoing these days?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.11,0:04:33.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,The same, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.71,0:04:35.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you concerned?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.45,0:04:36.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.48,0:04:40.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,But it's like we've been left hanging.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.46,0:04:44.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,It seems like the others are\Nstarting to accept her being gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.59,0:04:51.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,This means we can never go back\Nto the old Chor Tempest, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.06,0:04:54.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Para-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.63,0:04:57.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm keeping\Nan eye on you, Para-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.82,0:05:00.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.07,0:05:10.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rimone,\Nwe're heading for the pool now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.91,0:05:11.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.81,0:05:12.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.83,0:05:14.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're still young, so your endurance...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.65,0:05:16.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.79,0:05:19.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rimone! Hey, hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.42,0:05:23.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,Um, why don't we all take lunch first?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.60,0:05:38.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is something the matter,\NSibylla Paraietta?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.62,0:05:42.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is Sibylla Aurea's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.01,0:05:45.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm still repairing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.15,0:05:48.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,We had to rebuild\Nsome things from scratch...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.52,0:05:51.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,...so I had a hard time\Ngetting all the components.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.66,0:05:58.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Your wounds haven't healed yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.33,0:06:02.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,You haven't flown in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.41,0:06:23.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril! Hey, Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.65,0:06:27.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,You've been cooped up long enough.\NGet back on duty already!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.82,0:06:34.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,Chor Tempest just gets lame missions\Nbecause you won't come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.09,0:06:37.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't take much more!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.40,0:06:40.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is no place for us to be flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.87,0:06:45.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you listening, Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.21,0:06:48.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.68,0:06:58.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,You stubborn mule!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.50,0:07:16.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Really, what a childish thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.75,0:07:29.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,I guess I'm in no position to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.09,0:07:44.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. There was\Nno need for you to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.94,0:07:46.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,No, I really didn't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.34,0:07:50.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,Really, what are\Nwe going to do with Aer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.75,0:07:53.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,She's troubling you, right?\NShall I make her stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.88,0:08:00.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,Of course, I'm sure\Nit's not going to be pretty...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.12,0:08:12.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril... Don't you think\Nit's time you made things clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.18,0:08:14.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Made what clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.23,0:08:17.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,Either way, we can't go on like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.80,0:08:20.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Won't you come back to the chor?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.90,0:08:28.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,If you decide to go to the Spring,\Nthen this time I'll accompany you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.05,0:08:29.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.31,0:08:34.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm still unsure myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.69,0:08:38.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,About going to the Spring...\Nand about flying Simouns.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.20,0:08:40.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't decide yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.06,0:08:41.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.43,0:08:44.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm fully aware that it's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.32,0:08:51.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,But I feel that no matter which choice\NI make, it would be a betrayal...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.24,0:08:52.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Betrayal?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.40,0:08:56.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's the feeling I get.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.31,0:09:06.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,You mean Amuria.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.62,0:09:15.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril... I've spent my life by your\Nside ever since we were children.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.22,0:09:17.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,I've always walked\Nthe same path as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.27,0:09:20.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's why I can say this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.20,0:09:24.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,Your place is in a Simoun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.50,0:09:31.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,Even if that means\Nyou'll have to betray Amuria...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.21,0:09:33.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't talk to me as if you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.27,0:09:38.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's not as simple as that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.27,0:09:48.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Leave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.56,0:11:04.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.03,0:11:07.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,She's overwhelmed, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.03,0:11:10.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,And you've been so worried\Nabout her, Para-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.28,0:11:26.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,But I don't see why she doesn't\Ntry to understand how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.89,0:11:29.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't like the way Neviril's acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.06,0:11:31.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't talk like you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.96,0:11:33.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,I do know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.63,0:11:36.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,In other words,\Nshe's just being childish, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.37,0:11:40.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,She's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.61,0:11:42.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then what's up with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.44,0:11:56.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sure, losing Amuria\Nwas a big blow to her...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.29,0:11:59.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,...but she's not\Nthe only one who misses her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.73,0:12:04.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Keeping herself holed up is really\Ncausing trouble for the rest of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.45,0:12:05.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Kaim.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.16,0:12:11.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I was out of line.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.23,0:12:14.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Para-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.63,0:12:17.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,What happened to your hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.61,0:12:20.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, I was cleaning something...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.21,0:12:23.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,You can't just leave them like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.30,0:12:26.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,I know! Could you wait a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.68,0:12:28.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,S-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.75,0:12:37.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,I see... My nails are starting to shine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.00,0:12:41.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aren't they? You've got such beautiful\Nfingers, so take care of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.06,0:12:43.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,...or Tempus Spatium will scold you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.20,0:12:49.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,You enjoy this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.75,0:12:53.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm getting to take care of you, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.31,0:12:55.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,And touch you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.48,0:12:57.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.12,0:13:05.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,I think she's just lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.22,0:13:09.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,We probably all are.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.46,0:13:12.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,All of us on this ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.23,0:13:16.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Lonely, probably... That's what I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.99,0:13:26.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.08,0:13:31.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, Para-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.04,0:13:34.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you lonely too, Para-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.45,0:13:38.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,Do I look that bad to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.85,0:13:40.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.15,0:13:44.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm asking because I'm lonely too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.36,0:13:49.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Para-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.10,0:13:59.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's hot in here, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.81,0:14:02.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then why don't\Nwe go where it's cooler?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.35,0:14:13.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,No change in the princess yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.40,0:14:15.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.62,0:14:19.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,It reminds me of the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.07,0:14:21.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Like a certain someone, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.46,0:14:28.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's not uncommon for a sibylla\Nto question her flight duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.80,0:14:34.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was the one who offered\Nyou a helping hand then, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.24,0:14:36.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,I haven't forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.27,0:14:38.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Vroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.89,0:14:40.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Pow-pow-pow-pow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.05,0:14:42.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Vroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.27,0:14:44.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,Vroom! Blam!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.46,0:14:47.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Pow-pow-pow-pow!\NI see some more coming at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.53,0:14:50.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Blam! Pow-pow-pow-pow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.49,0:14:54.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm not scared of that lame attack!\NLet's see you hit us if you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.63,0:14:57.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Vroom! Pow-pow-pow-pow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.25,0:14:59.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey! Para-sama!\NEnemy to your right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.51,0:15:03.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,Strafe them with\Nthe machine gun! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.84,0:15:04.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.24,0:15:06.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,Pow-pow-pow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.44,0:15:08.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wow, Para-sama! 100 of 100!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.65,0:15:10.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,Pow-pow-pow! Pow-pow-pow-pow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.14,0:15:14.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Another group of enemies\Nbeyond the clouds! Ray Ri Majon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.10,0:15:23.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,Kaim?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.99,0:15:26.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, Para-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.82,0:15:30.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's do a Ri Majon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.41,0:15:49.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,Strange... We always do that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.00,0:16:07.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh! We've got to turn it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.32,0:16:13.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Kaim!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.02,0:16:31.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Big Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.09,0:16:33.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Big Sister Kaim...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.33,0:17:07.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was always by her side.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.56,0:17:11.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'd decided to stay by her side forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.70,0:17:16.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,And before I knew it, being near\Nher had become a natural thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.38,0:17:30.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,How arrogant of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.35,0:17:35.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Thinking I was the only\None she could ever lean on...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.42,0:17:39.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,I thought that it was obvious...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.60,0:17:54.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,In that moment,\NI wasn't the only one who felt pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.71,0:17:59.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is that the reason why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.05,0:18:10.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Para-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.23,0:18:11.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's not do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.31,0:18:12.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.00,0:18:15.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because you're still a child, Kaim.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.54,0:18:17.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,What? I'm not a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.47,0:18:18.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,You are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.46,0:18:19.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.43,0:18:22.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're all children.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.57,0:18:27.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's why we try to heal our wounds\Nbut end up creating new wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.14,0:18:32.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.55,0:18:34.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,Good night, Kaim.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.42,0:18:41.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.46,0:18:46.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Jeez, why can't you\Nsee how I feel, Para-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.47,0:19:00.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.61,0:19:04.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril! Just listen to me\Nfor a second, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.15,0:19:05.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.83,0:19:07.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.95,0:19:11.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,I swear...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.85,0:19:16.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Now that it's come to this, I'll drag\Nyou out if it's the last thing I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.49,0:19:18.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,Paraietta.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.87,0:19:21.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer, I'd like to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.20,0:19:30.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,It doesn't look like we're\Nabout to do any talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.94,0:19:33.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,Didn't you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.31,0:19:35.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,The maju pool can\Nbe used for this too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.51,0:19:43.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,So how did I end up\Nhaving to face you like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.87,0:19:49.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.30,0:20:05.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,The reason Neviril refuses to decide\Nisn't just because of Amuria.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.51,0:20:08.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,I see now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.99,0:20:12.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,It was also out of\Nrespect for my feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.51,0:20:19.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril, I'm sorry.\NI didn't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.62,0:20:23.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,But just let me say this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.60,0:20:27.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't feel as though\Nyou've betrayed me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.25,0:20:35.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,And I appreciate how\Nconsiderate you're being.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.87,0:20:38.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.44,0:20:40.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.58,0:20:47.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's why I'll put my hopes on\None who can surpass Amuria!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.27,0:20:58.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,I've got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.69,0:21:02.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.76,0:21:03.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.74,0:21:11.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're open!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.98,0:21:12.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.21,0:21:23.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is that good enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.60,0:21:40.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer! Go and pair up with Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.97,0:21:45.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,You don't have to tell me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.48,0:21:54.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, Floe...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.89,0:21:56.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.62,0:21:59.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,So what happens next?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.04,0:22:00.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.32,0:22:05.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,The birds who rest their wings...\NYou said they couldn't fly forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.10,0:22:07.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,They'll fly again of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.59,0:22:08.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,They will?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.80,0:22:13.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's right. Because birds\Nwere born to fly in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.17,0:22:16.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,To fly in the sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.74,0:22:23.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,If she's resting her wings, it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.82,0:22:30.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,But a bird who can't fly\Nbecause she's been wounded...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.86,0:22:32.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,...has no hope of survival.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.23,0:22:47.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,It is played by my wounds...\Nthe song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.94,0:22:52.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let it ring out over\Nthe grieving universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.18,0:22:59.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Can we change tomorrow?\NDon't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.25,0:23:06.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to let you know\Nhow my heart's overflowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.66,0:23:19.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,"I want to get closer to you."\N"I want to feel your pulse."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.74,0:23:24.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was too defiant,\Nand I took the long way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.91,0:23:28.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,The blue moon is swaying silently.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.92,0:23:32.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,My true heart's desire is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.89,0:23:38.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't reach you.\NMy tears of pain trickle down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.79,0:23:44.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Soar away into the sky, song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.34,0:23:47.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,Carrying my love that came too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.80,0:23:53.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,What can I do to change tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.44,0:23:59.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just hold on to "now" the way it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.08,0:24:06.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,To Be Continued
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.88,0:24:07.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,In order to sign a peace treaty...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.92,0:24:11.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,...delegations from the highlands and\Nthe Arcus Prima are about to meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.68,0:24:16.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,Next time on Simoun...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.66,0:24:18.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,Over International Waters.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.51,0:24:20.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Over International Waters
